        <p class="place-description">
            <span class="short-text" data-en="Ethiopia's climate varies by region. October - March is ideal for most regions with dry weather..." data-am="የኢትዮጵያ አየር አለፍ በክልል ይለያያል። ከጥቅምት እስከ መጋቢት በብዛት ክልሎች ለደረቅ የአየር ሁኔታ...">Ethiopia's climate varies by region. October - March is ideal for most regions with dry weather...</span>
            <span class="full-text" style="display: none;" data-en="Ethiopia's climate varies by region. October - March is ideal for most regions with dry weather. September - November offers harvest season with green landscapes. March - May provides spring season with pleasant weather. June - August is rainy season with lush green scenery." data-am="የኢትዮጵያ አየር አለፍ በክልል ይለያያል። ከጥቅምት እስከ መጋቢት በብዛት ክልሎች ለደረቅ የአየር ሁኔታ ተስማሚ ነው። ከመስከረም እስከ ኅዳር የእርሻ ወቅት አረንጓዴ መልክዮችን ይሰጣል። ከጥቅምት እስከ ግንቦት የጸደይ ወቅት ከባድ የአየር ሁኔታን ይሰጣል። ከሰኔ እስከ ነሐሴ የጥሩ ወቅት አረንጓዴ መልክዮችን ይሰጣል።">Ethiopia's climate varies by region. October - March is ideal for most regions with dry weather. September - November offers harvest season with green landscapes. March - May provides spring season with pleasant weather. June - August is rainy season with lush green scenery.</span>
        </p>
