        <p class="place-description">
            <span class="short-text" data-en="Getting around Ethiopia includes flying with Ethiopian Airlines, comfortable long-distance buses..." data-am="በኢትዮጵያ መዞር የኢትዮጵያ አየር መንገድ፣ ምቹ የሆኑ ረጅም ርቀት ባስዎችን ያካትታል...">Getting around Ethiopia includes flying with Ethiopian Airlines, comfortable long-distance buses...</span>
            <span class="full-text" style="display: none;" data-en="Getting around Ethiopia includes flying with Ethiopian Airlines connecting major cities daily, comfortable long-distance buses between cities, 4WD car rentals recommended for rural areas, taxis available in cities (agree on price first), and domestic flights that save time between distant destinations." data-am="በኢትዮጵያ መዞር የኢትዮጵያ አየር መንገድ ዋና ዋና ከተሞችን የሚያገናኝ በየው ቀን በመብረር፣ በከተማዎች መካከል ምቹ የሆኑ ረጅም ርቀት ባስዎች፣ ለገጠር አካባቢዎች 4WD መኪና ኪራይ የሚመከር፣ በከተማዎች ውስጥ ታክሲዎች (ዋጋውን መፈረም)፣ እና በርቀት ያሉ መዳረሻዎች መካከል ጊዜን የሚቆጥቡ የአገር ውስጥ በረራዎችን ያካትታል።">Getting around Ethiopia includes flying with Ethiopian Airlines connecting major cities daily, comfortable long-distance buses between cities, 4WD car rentals recommended for rural areas, taxis available in cities (agree on price first), and domestic flights that save time between distant destinations.</span>
        </p>
