        <p class="place-description">
            <span class="short-text" data-en="Essential items include comfortable walking shoes, light layers for temperature changes..." data-am="አስፈላጊ እቃዎች የሚመጡት ምቹ የሆኑ የመንገድ ጫማዎች፣ ለየትላተኛው ለውጥ ቀለሞች...">Essential items include comfortable walking shoes, light layers for temperature changes...</span>
            <span class="full-text" style="display: none;" data-en="Essential items include comfortable walking shoes, light layers for temperature changes, sun protection (hat, sunscreen, sunglasses), camera and extra batteries, first aid kit and personal medications, power adapter (Type E, 220V), and reusable water bottle." data-am="አስፈላጊ እቃዎች የሚመጡት ምቹ የሆኑ የመንገድ ጫማዎች፣ ለየትላተኛው ለውጥ ቀለሞች፣ ከፀሐይ መከላከያ (ካፒ፣ ሱና፣ ናማ መነጽር)፣ ካሜራ እና ተጨማሪ ባትሪ፣ የመጀመሪያ እርዳታ ኪት እና የግል መድኃኒቶች፣ የኃይል አዳፒር (ዓይነት E, 220V)፣ እና እንደገና መጠቀሚያ ውሃ ጠርሙ።">Essential items include comfortable walking shoes, light layers for temperature changes, sun protection (hat, sunscreen, sunglasses), camera and extra batteries, first aid kit and personal medications, power adapter (Type E, 220V), and reusable water bottle.</span>
