        <p class="place-description">
            <span class="short-text" data-en="Must-try dishes include Injera (sour flatbread, staple food), Doro Wat (spicy chicken stew)..." data-am="የሚመግቡት ምግቦች እንጀራ (ጠባታ ዳቦ፣ ዋና ምግብ)፣ ዶሮ ዋት (በረማዊ ዶሮ ስጋ)...">Must-try dishes include Injera (sour flatbread, staple food), Doro Wat (spicy chicken stew)...</span>
            <span class="full-text" style="display: none;" data-en="Must-try dishes include Injera (sour flatbread, staple food), Doro Wat (spicy chicken stew), Kitfo (raw minced beef with spices), Tibs (grilled meat or vegetables), Shiro (chickpea stew), and Ethiopian Coffee with traditional ceremony." data-am="የሚመግቡት ምግቦች እንጀራ (ጠባታ ዳቦ፣ ዋና ምግብ)፣ ዶሮ ዋት (በረማዊ ዶሮ ስጋ)፣ ክትፎ (ከሚሊዮን የተሰረቀ እንቁላል ስጋ)፣ ቲብስ (የተቀቀለ ስጋ ወይም አትክልቶች)፣ ሽሮ (የሽሮ ስጋ)፣ እና በባህላዊ ሥነ ሥርዓት የኢትዮጵያ ቡና።">Must-try dishes include Injera (sour flatbread, staple food), Doro Wat (spicy chicken stew), Kitfo (raw minced beef with spices), Tibs (grilled meat or vegetables), Shiro (chickpea stew), and Ethiopian Coffee with traditional ceremony.</span>
