        <p class="place-description">
            <span class="short-text" data-en="Important advice includes bargaining politely in markets, asking permission before photographing people..." data-am="አስፈላጊ እርዳታ በገበያዎች በአደባባይ መ�ደር፣ ሰዎችን ከመንኳፍፍ በፊት ፍቀድ...">Important advice includes bargaining politely in markets, asking permission before photographing people...</span>
