            <span class="full-text" style="display: none;" data-en="Respect local customs includes dressing modestly especially at religious sites, removing shoes before entering churches, accepting food and drinks with right hand, not pointing with index finger, respecting elders and religious leaders, and asking before photographing ceremonies." data-am="የአካባቢ ባህሎችን መከበር በተለይ በሃይማኖታዊ ቦታዎች በአንደኛው መልክ መልበስ፣ ወደ አብይቶች ከመግባት በፊት ጫማዎችን ማውጣት፣ ምግብና መጠጣትን በቀኝ እጅ መቀበል፣ በአማማይ ጣቶ መጠቅለል፣ አባቶችን እና የሃይማኖት መሪዎችን መከበር፣ እና ክብርተኞችን ከመንኳፍፍ በፊት መጠየቅ።">Respect local customs includes dressing modestly especially at religious sites, removing shoes before entering churches, accepting food and drinks with right hand, not pointing with index finger, respecting elders and religious leaders, and asking before photographing ceremonies.</span>
