        <h3><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> <span data-en="Health & Safety" data-am="ጤናና ደህንነት">Health & Safety</span></h3>
        <p class="place-description">
            <span class="short-text" data-en="Stay healthy includes getting travel insurance, vaccinations for Hepatitis A, Typhoid, Yellow Fever..." data-am="ጤንኛ መሆን የጉዞ ኢንሹራንስ መውሰድ፣ ለሄፓታይቲስ ኤ፣ ታይፎይድ፣ ቢሮ ፈቨር...">Stay healthy includes getting travel insurance, vaccinations for Hepatitis A, Typhoid, Yellow Fever...</span>
            <span class="full-text" style="display: none;" data-en="Stay healthy includes getting travel insurance, vaccinations for Hepatitis A, Typhoid, Yellow Fever, malaria prophylaxis for lowland areas, avoiding tap water and drinking bottled, carrying basic medications, and emergency number is 911." data-am="ጤንኛ መሆን የጉዞ ኢንሹራንስ መውሰድ፣ ለሄፓታይቲስ ኤ፣ ታይፎይድ፣ ቢሮ ፈቨር ቫክሲኖች፣ ለዝቅተኛ አካባቢዎች ማላሪያ መድኃኒት፣ የኩሽና ውሃ መጠጣትና የተዘጋውን መጠጣት፣ መሰረታዊ መድኃኒቶች መያዣ፣ እና የአስቸኳይ ቁጥር 911።">Stay healthy includes getting travel insurance, vaccinations for Hepatitis A, Typhoid, Yellow Fever, malaria prophylaxis for lowland areas, avoiding tap water and drinking bottled, carrying basic medications, and emergency number is 911.</span>
        </p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-read-more" onclick="toggleReadMore(this)" data-en="Read More" data-am="ተጨማሪ ያንብቡ">Read More</button>
